        <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Personality That Fits Your Culture</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">DISC, Big Five, or MBTI mapped to agent behavior. Not a generic chatbot.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-otp-900/60 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 reveal">
